Name: Mighty Planes
Title: Boeing 747-8F
Desc: The Boeing 747-8F transports the gear of Formula E's 10 racing teams to cities around the world.
LongDescription: Transporting the gear of Formula E's 10 electric-powered racing teams to cities around the world across more than 50,000 total kilometres in the greenest way imaginable is no easy task; for air transport, DHL uses Boeing 747 or 777 aircraft.
